title: RNA-26-08_1
characteristics_ch1.1: cell type: Adipose Mesenchymal Stem Cells
treatment_protocol_ch1: At 6,7&8 passage, 2×10^6 cells were seeded and incubated overnight. On the next day, cells were fed with new medium for another 48 h and the result medium was collected as conditioned medium (CM).
growth_protocol_ch1: Human adipose mesenchymal stem cells (hAMSCs) were cultured in a complete α-MEM medium
extract_protocol_ch1: Exosomes were isolated using Exoquick-TC kit (SBI, USA) and the exosomal-miRNA was isolated using SeraMir Exosomal miRNA isolation kit (SBI, USA)
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Libraries were constructed from smRNA using the TruSeq Small RNA Library Prep Kit following  manufacturer's protocols.
data_processing: Illumina RTA (Real Time Analysis. v1.18) software used for basecalling.
data_processing.1: Sequenced reads were trimmed for adaptor sequence with cutadapt 1.9.dev3.
data_processing.2: To estimate expression levels, the smRNA-Seq reads were mapped to the pre-miRNA and mature miRNA sequence of Homo sapiens using bowtie 1.1.1.
data_processing.3: The pre-miRNA and mature miRNA sequence of Homo sapiens (hg19) were downloaded from miRBase (release 21). The read counts of mature miRNA were calculated from mapping results.
data_processing.5: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: tab-delimited text files include read count for each samples.
contact_laboratory: Germ Cell and Regenerative Bio-medicine Lab.
